+++++ Special Containment Procedures:
Instances of SCP-x028 are to be kept in locked storage room LMC in Site-814.

+++++ Description: 
SCP-x028 is a series of plastic sculptures, designed as amusement park decorations. These sculptures, known as “Giggles” are very simple, consisting of a colored body in the shape of a pill, with a flattened bottom, and a pair of cartoon eyes. Instances of SCP-x028 can be any color, with red and green being the most common. The backside of SCP-x028 instances has an inscription reading “Property of Doctor Wondertainment.”
[[/div]]



